631
01:35:06,993 --> 01:35:08,703
da locum Spiritui Sancto,

632
01:35:09,245 --> 01:35:14,417
per hoc signum sanctae Cruci
Jesu Christi Domini nostri:

633
01:35:15,001 --> 01:35:20,089
